{"tid":1308754,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蔡英文總統過境紐約 下榻飯店外爆激烈衝突1送醫1被捕","createTime":"2019-07-12T03:30:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-12T03:36:51.000Z","uid":28765,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"03018ae2d5b8461ade3eb250fe797402c72a5717","tid":1308754,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T03:30:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpX8sHwW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpX8sHwW.jpg&h=191e5e81&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpX8sHwW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpX8sHwW.jpg&h=191e5e81&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n兩派人馬隔街互嗆，演變成激烈衝突、大打出手，雙方多人受傷，最後1人被逮補、1人送醫。（路透）<br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕蔡英文總統11日展開自由民主永續之旅，首站過境美國紐約，蔡總統下榻的飯店外聚集支持者和反對者，兩派人馬隔街互嗆，演變成激烈衝突、大打出手，雙方多人受傷，最後1人被逮捕、1人送醫。<br />\n<br />\n綜合媒體報導，蔡英文在當地時間下午4時30分抵達曼哈頓下榻的飯店，但飯店外從下午2時就開始聚集支持者和反對者，雙方隔著42街隔空互嗆，一方為親台團體，高喊「支持蔡英文、支持台灣人擁有主權」；另一方則為親中國團體，揮舞五星旗，反對台獨、要求蔡英文下台。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n報導提及，原本雙方僅是隔著42街叫囂，但隨後雙方火氣上升，演變成激烈肢體衝突，雙方大打出手，最終造成多人受傷，1人送醫、1人遭到警方逮捕。<br />\n<br />\n蔡英文在當地時間下午4時許抵達曼哈頓下榻飯店，受到支持者熱烈歡迎，兩派沒有再發生衝突。對於在下榻飯店前發生支持與反對人馬兩派大打出手，蔡總統說，她有聽到一些，在民主社會裡面，還是以理性的方式表達不同意見，也希望大家在表達不同意見的時候也可以保持理性。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/2850398\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F2850398&d=tO8FO7ZpCqi602%2BiQgdm0FDHT90Y5dJ0llo76wtTvPU%3D&h=bbd00e5a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F2850398&h=107c79c9\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/2850398</a>"},{"pid":"7893f3cf08ce150e3de638219b643cda76f4e5c3","tid":1308754,"uid":8441,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T03:31:21.000Z","msg":"大陸人要求台灣總統下台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0f84b5f50dd42a21857c39eb15054489c3170ac","tid":1308754,"uid":151256,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T03:31:38.000Z","msg":"喺美國支持中國 on9"},{"pid":"d46d5d7031c05cbf13ac180605755c00dee72a15","tid":1308754,"uid":261332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7893f3cf08ce150e3de638219b643cda76f4e5c3","tid":1308754,"uid":8441,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T03:31:21.000Z","msg":"大陸人要求台灣總統下台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T03:32:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1fa84824dd58d0a43843ebc9396b8f906801571","tid":1308754,"uid":261332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7893f3cf08ce150e3de638219b643cda76f4e5c3","tid":1308754,"uid":8441,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T03:31:21.000Z","msg":"大陸人要求台灣總統下台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T03:32:22.000Z","msg":"不過美國佬未必識分"},{"pid":"c055391fdccc65d51f6e6f19802cb9123dd7d3cf","tid":1308754,"uid":60655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7893f3cf08ce150e3de638219b643cda76f4e5c3","tid":1308754,"uid":8441,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T03:31:21.000Z","msg":"大陸人要求台灣總統下台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T03:32:35.000Z","msg":"又話武統台灣"},{"pid":"c2d5dce78b9870d32940e638a1a1f8cdc79b94d7","tid":1308754,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"c